Products listed for sale on the website are not guaranteed to be in stock. The ability to purchase any item depends on the availability of the item. Silhouette America® does not offer rain checks, layaways, or the ability to hold or reserve products.
All bundles and items listed in the “Clearance” section are only available while supplies last. Silhouette America® reserves the right to discontinue products from being sold through the website with or without notice. Bundles containing multiple product offerings cannot be adjusted to substitute, add, remove, change, or otherwise alter the content of the bundle offering.
13. Promotions
Sales promotions may be offered periodically through
www.silhouetteamerica.com
. Please refer to the Terms and Conditions posted for each sale for further details specific to the promotion. It is your responsibility to read the applicable Terms and Conditions to determine whether or not your participation will be valid or restricted, and to determine any requirements specific to the promotion. In most cases, a promotional code is provided and must be applied in the shopping cart prior to checkout in order to apply the promotional sale pricing.
Promotional pricing is available during the advertised promotional period only. Promotional pricing cannot be reserved for: out of stock items, issues with your Silhouette account, concerns with payment information, or other concerns resulting from anything which cannot reasonably be controlled by Silhouette America® that may occur during the promotional period preventing order completion.
Silhouette America® at its sole discretion may make special exceptions to extend promotional pricing to price match Silhouette promotional sales and/or provide a refund toward orders of products purchased directly from
www.silhouetteamerica.com
upon notification to Silhouette Support if a) an order was completed within 24 hours prior to the start of a promotional sale period, or b) an order was completed within 24 hours after the end of the promotional sale period due to a technical issue outside of your control which prevented successful order completion during the sale period. Examples of technical issues outside of your control may include: a server issue, or other error with the Silhouette America website service. Examples of issues that would not apply to this exception would be: your account was on hold, you did not yet have sufficient funds to purchase product.
14. Payments
All payments for products purchased through the website must be made using a valid credit card. Silhouette America® is not liable for any loss caused by any unauthorized use of your credit card by a third party in connection with our website.
Any attempt at fraudulent activity, including any activity suspected of fraudulent activity, will result in having your Silhouette account frozen or terminated and further may block your access to the website, which action shall be at the sole discretion of Silhouette America®. Silhouette America® is entitled to report such activity to any relevant authorities or entities, and is further entitled to engage in civil and/or criminal prosecution.
You irrevocably authorize Silhouette America®, as necessary, to use third-party electronic payment processors and/or financial institutions to process financial transactions, and agree that Silhouette America® may instruct third-party electronic payment processors and/or financial institutions on your behalf in accordance with your submitted orders.
15. Gift Cards
Silhouette America® Gift Cards (“E-Gift Card”) may only be used for purchases made online at
www.silhouetteamerica.com
. A Silhouette account is required to redeem a Gift Card. Gift Cards are not redeemable or refundable for cash. Gift Cards may not be resold. Unless stated otherwise, Gift Cards shall not expire and may not be redeemed for shipments outside the website’s allowable shipping area (see section 20 “Shipping” below). Additional payment is required if the purchase price exceeds the value of the Gift Card. Lost or stolen Gift Cards will not be replaced.
Any term or condition of this card is void where prohibited by law. These terms and conditions are subject to change without notice. Purchase of or use of a Silhouette America® Gift Card constitutes agreement to the terms listed herein.
16. Orders
The Silhouette America® website provides the ability to purchase products, both physical and digital. You are able to add products to your cart that you wish to order by clicking on the “Add to Cart” button located on the product details page. Placing an item in your shopping cart does not reserve the item. Products are reserved only upon successfully completing the checkout process. Successfully completed orders will receive an automated email confirming order placement.
All orders are final once you have completed the checkout process and paid for the order. Orders cannot be altered to have items added, removed, or individually canceled once the order has been placed. If you wish to cancel an order, you must contact Silhouette Support within 24 hours of order placement. Cancellation requests may take up to 48 hours to complete. Requests to cancel do not guarantee successful cancellation. In the case your order has shipped prior to successful cancellation, it is your responsibility to refuse the delivery or return the order per the
Product Return Policy
.
17. Our Right To Not Accept Or Cancel Your Order
Silhouette America® reserves the right to refuse any order for whatever reason it
                        deems appropriate. We also reserve the right to cancel and refund any order for any of following
                        reasons, which include but are not limited to: download content no longer available; you do not
                        meet all of conditions of these Terms of Use; you do not have the ability to properly download
                        the purchased content; or there has been an error in the price quote as noted in the section 25
                        (“Pricing”) of these Terms of Use. We further reserve the right to cancel your order for any of
                        following reasons, which include but are not limited to: your billing information is not correct
                        or cannot be verified; your order is flagged by our security measures as being suspicious or
                        fraudulent; or funds are not properly received.
18. Pricing
All product pricing listed on this website is in US Dollars (USD). Product prices listed on this website are subject to change without notice. All pricing listed at the moment of purchase is the applicable price that will be charged, except in the case where pricing information on the website may contain an error. Silhouette America® is not bound by offers listed in error and reserves the right to make corrections for any such errors and/or cancel orders where there have been errors in pricing.
Sales tax is not included in the listed price of any download content. Sales tax is assessed based on your zip or postal code for orders placed within select areas in the United States, and will be applied per applicable sales tax law where required. You can view the presence of sales tax and sales tax information prior to check-out while viewing your Shopping Cart.
Silhouette America® does not offer price matching on products purchased from other websites or store locations, or for shipping costs offered from other websites.
19. Shipping
Orders placed on
www.silhouetteamerica.com
can only be shipped within the United States, Canada, and US Territories (Guam, Northern Mariana Islands, Puerto Rico, and Virgin Islands). Canadian shipments are subject to import duties, taxes, and/or customs fees which are imposed by the local government once the package is received. You are solely responsible for any such fees.
Silhouette America® does not ship to hotels or other temporary locations. Any returned orders resulting from shipping to temporary locations will result in a restocking fee of up to 20%.
Shipping rates are based on the weight of products being purchased along with your zip or postal code (US only), or other allowable shipping area location. You can get an estimated shipping cost prior to check-out while viewing your Shopping Cart. Exact shipping cost is calculated on the final checkout page prior to placing the order. Silhouette America® cannot be held responsible for discrepancies between estimated shipping costs displayed in the shopping cart page and the actual shipping costs displayed during final check out. By proceeding to place your order, you confirm that you understand that your order may be split between more than one Silhouette fulfillment center dependent upon product availability and you consent to be charged additional shipping costs associated with such multiple shipments, when applicable.
Allow 7 - 12 days for delivery of any order placed through
www.silhouetteamerica.com
. Silhouette America® cannot guarantee delivery by a specific date. Actual ship times are dependent upon the delivery service of the shipping carrier being used and may be affected or increased during promotional periods. Silhouette America® does not offer expedited shipping options. An automated email with tracking information will be issued to your Silhouette account email address once your order is shipped. You may also sign into your Silhouette account and click on the “my account” link. From here you may view any recent order and tracking information (present if your order has been shipped).
Silhouette America® cannot adjust your shipping address once the order is delivered to the carrier. You are solely responsible for the risk of loss for products purchased through
www.silhouetteamerica.com
once they are delivered to the carrier.
