Club Silhouette
Club Silhouette Program
Club Silhouette memberships are a premium service offered by Silhouette America® which provide special services and considerations to club members, including monthly digital content, periodic product shipments, and discounts on orders placed at
www.silhouetteamerica.com
A membership to Club Silhouette is not required to access the Silhouette America® website.
You must have a Silhouette account in order to sign up for a Club Silhouette Membership at
Join Club Silhouette
.
A. Membership Terms
Club Silhouette entitles you to membership benefits from the moment you activate your membership by submitting your payment details. By submitting these details, you accept the terms of the Club Silhouette membership and agree to the use of your payment information according to our Privacy Policy.
B. Continuing Membership
If you do not cancel your membership before the membership period ends, you will be charged a Club Silhouette membership fee depending on the membership type selected during the sign-up process. A yearly (12-month) membership can be purchased for $9.99 per month. Customers selecting to pay up-front for a yearly (12-month) membership can purchase a yearly subscription at $99.99, meaning that an additional discount is given to customers who choose to pay their subscription up-front at sign-up rather than month-to-month.
