All refurbished units receive a full inspection to ensure proper working condition, appearance, and quality. All refurbished units come with a 30-day limited warranty to cover any defects that may arise during that time frame. In all approved warranty cases, a like model will be issued. Silhouette America cannot substitute alternate machine models or issue monetary reimbursement or other forms of compensation.
Replacement of Limited Edition Products
Limited edition products, including alternate product color variants, are covered under warranty as stated in the "Limited Warranty" section above. However, limited edition products, including color variants, may not be able to be replaced with an identical unit. After full evaluation of the returned unit by our warranty department, if a manufacturer's defect is confirmed, a new replacement unit of like or similar product variation will be issued, dependent upon available inventory. If inventory of a like or similar product variant is unavailable, Silhouette America shall issue a new, available, standard, nonexclusive unit. If a manufacturer's defect cannot be confirmed, a refurbished (like-new) unit of like or similar product variation will be issued, dependent upon available inventory. If inventory of like or similar product variant is unavailable, Silhouette America shall issue an available, standard, nonexclusive, refurbished (like-new) unit.
A repair option may be offered as an alternative for limited edition (color variation) units.
